<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Popovics Lab | Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia Research</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The Popovics Lab studies benign prostatic hyperplasia, urinary function, inflammation, fibrosis, and prostate tissue remodeling through translational research." />

  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #123044;
      --teal: #29989a;
      --teal-light: #dff3f2;
      --teal-soft: #eefafa;
      --teal-dark: #1f797c;
      --red: #9b2f2f;
      --red-soft: #f5e7e7;
      --paper: #ffffff;
      --ink: #17252b;
      --muted: #5b6c72;
      --line: rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.24);
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.10);
      --radius: 18px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(24px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes floatSoft {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-12px);
      }
    }

    @keyframes glowPulse {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 0.68;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1.04);
      }
    }

    @keyframes lineGrow {
      from {
        transform: scaleX(0);
      }
      to {
        transform: scaleX(1);
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.001ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        scroll-behavior: auto !important;
        transition-duration: 0.001ms !important;
      }
    }

    body {
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--paper);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .site-shell {
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f6fbfb 58%, #ffffff 100%);
      background-size: 42px 42px, 42px 42px, auto;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.06);
    }

   .nav {
  min-height: 122px;
  padding: 16px 0 24px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 28px;
}

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--navy);
      white-space: nowrap;
      padding: 0;
      border-radius: 0;
      background: transparent;
      border: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

  .brand img {
  width: min(360px, 62vw);
  max-height: 92px;
  height: auto;
  object-fit: contain;
  display: block;
}
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      opacity: 1;
      transition: 180ms ease;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: white;
      background: var(--teal);
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: 180ms ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .button-primary {
      color: white;
      background: var(--teal);
      border-color: var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.24);
    }

    .button-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      background: var(--teal-dark);
      border-color: var(--teal-dark);
    }

    .button-secondary {
      color: var(--teal-dark);
      background: white;
      border-color: var(--teal);
    }

    .button-secondary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      color: white;
      background: var(--red);
      border-color: var(--red);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 86px 0 72px;
    }

    .hero::before,
    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero::before {
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      left: -90px;
      top: 80px;
      background: rgba(60, 155, 155, 0.12);
      animation: glowPulse 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .hero::after {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      right: 6%;
      bottom: 36px;
      background: rgba(143, 47, 47, 0.10);
      animation: glowPulse 8s ease-in-out infinite 1.2s;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 54px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--red);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 38px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--teal);
      border-radius: 999px;
      transform-origin: left;
      animation: lineGrow 0.8s ease both 0.25s;
    }

    h1 {
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6.7vw, 5.9rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both 0.1s;
    }

    h1::after {
      content: "";
      display: block;
      width: 112px;
      height: 7px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal) 0 68%, var(--red) 68% 100%);
    }

    .hero-lede {
      font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.42rem);
      color: #334650;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both 0.2s;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 650px;
      font-size: 1.03rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both 0.3s;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both 0.4s;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 650px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.75s ease both 0.5s;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.64);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .visual-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 520px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: white;
      border: 3px solid var(--teal);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both 0.3s;
    }

    .visual-main {
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 484px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(31, 121, 124, 0.92), rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.76)),
        url("/images/hero-microscopy.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .visual-main::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 28% 26%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22), transparent 8rem),
        linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.72) 100%);
    }

    .visual-text {
      position: relative;
      color: white;
    }

    .visual-text h2 {
      font-size: 2.15rem;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .visual-text p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      max-width: 380px;
    }

    .floating-card {
      position: absolute;
      right: -20px;
      top: 44px;
      width: 238px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 18px;
      background: white;
      border: 3px solid var(--red);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.14);
      animation: floatSoft 5.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .floating-card .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(60, 155, 155, 0.12);
      color: var(--teal-dark);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .floating-card strong {
      color: var(--navy);
      display: block;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .floating-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .section-heading.center {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--teal-dark);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-heading p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.06rem;
    }

    .research-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .research-card {
      min-height: 290px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 26px;
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.06);
      transition: 180ms ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .research-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      height: 7px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      top: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal) 0 76%, var(--red) 76% 100%);
    }

    .research-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 55px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.12);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      color: white;
      background: var(--teal);
      border-bottom: 5px solid var(--red);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .research-card h3 {
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 1.34rem;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .research-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .feature-band {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-dark), var(--navy));
      color: white;
      padding: 42px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 38px;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    }

    .feature-band::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(60, 155, 155, 0.30), transparent 18rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 70%, rgba(143, 47, 47, 0.26), transparent 18rem);
    }

    .feature-band > * {
      position: relative;
    }

    .feature-band h2 {
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .feature-band p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .feature-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .feature-item strong {
      display: block;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .feature-item span {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .people-preview {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.82fr 1.18fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .portrait-card {
      min-height: 420px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.12), rgba(41, 152, 154, 0.18)),
        url("/images/team-photo.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      border: 3px solid var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.08);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .portrait-card::after {
      content: "Lab photo placeholder";
      position: absolute;
      left: 22px;
      bottom: 22px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .people-text {
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .people-text p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      font-size: 1.04rem;
    }

    .mini-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .mini-card {
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: rgba(238, 250, 250, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .mini-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .mini-card span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.91rem;
    }

    .news-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .news-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.07);
    }

    .news-image {
      height: 160px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(60, 155, 155, 0.82), rgba(18, 48, 68, 0.82)),
        url("/images/news-placeholder.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .news-body {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .date {
      color: var(--teal-dark);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .news-body h3 {
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.18;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.13rem;
    }

    .news-body p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .cta {
      padding-bottom: 92px;
    }

    .cta-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 44px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal-dark));
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border: 4px solid white;
    }

    .cta-card h2 {
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .cta-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .cta-card .button {
      background: white;
      color: var(--navy);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--teal-dark);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      padding: 44px 0;
      border-top: 8px solid var(--red);
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      color: white;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 930px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .feature-band,
      .people-preview,
      .cta-card,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .visual-card {
        min-height: 440px;
      }

      .floating-card {
        right: 18px;
        top: 18px;
      }

      .research-grid,
      .news-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .cta-card {
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .container {
        width: min(100% - 28px, 1160px);
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 56px;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .button {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .feature-band,
      .cta-card,
      .people-text {
        padding: 26px;
        border-radius: 26px;
      }

      .mini-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="site-shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="container nav">
        <a href="#top" class="brand" aria-label="Popovics Lab home">
          <img src="/images/popovics-lab-logo.png" alt="The Popovics Lab logo">
        </a>

        <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Main navigation">
          <a href="#research">Research</a>
          <a href="#approach">Approach</a>
          <a href="#people">People</a>
          <a href="#news">News</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia Research</div>
            <h1>Redefining how we understand benign prostate disease.</h1>
            <p class="hero-lede">We study how inflammation, aging, cellular stress, and tissue remodeling contribute to benign prostatic hyperplasia and lower urinary tract symptoms.</p>
            <p class="hero-copy">The Popovics Lab combines human prostate tissues, molecular biology, histology, imaging, and translational models to uncover mechanisms that may shape better treatment strategies for benign prostate disease.</p>

            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="button button-primary" href="#research">Explore our research</a>
              <a class="button button-secondary" href="#people">Meet the team</a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-stats" aria-label="Research themes">
              <div class="stat">
                <strong>BPH & LUTS</strong>
                <span>Mechanisms behind prostate enlargement and urinary dysfunction.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <strong>Inflammation</strong>
                <span>Immune and stress pathways that reshape prostate tissue.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <strong>Fibrosis</strong>
                <span>Extracellular matrix remodeling and epithelial-stromal crosstalk.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="visual-card" aria-label="Microscopy-inspired laboratory visual">
            <div class="visual-main">
              <div class="visual-text">
                <h2>From tissue to mechanism.</h2>
                <p>Connecting what we see under the microscope to the biological pathways that drive disease.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="floating-card">
              <span class="tag">Translational Science</span>
              <strong>Human tissue. Imaging. Molecular insight.</strong>
              <p>A modern lab site that feels alive, visual, and research-forward.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="research">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-heading center">
            <div class="section-kicker">Research Focus</div>
            <h2>Understanding benign prostate disease from multiple angles.</h2>
            <p>Our work investigates the cellular and molecular changes that contribute to BPH progression, urinary symptoms, and prostate tissue remodeling.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="research-grid">
            <article class="research-card">
              <div class="icon">01</div>
              <h3>Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</h3>
              <p>We investigate the biological processes that contribute to prostate enlargement and lower urinary tract symptoms, with a focus on patient-relevant mechanisms.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="research-card">
              <div class="icon">02</div>
              <h3>Inflammation & Cellular Stress</h3>
              <p>We explore how inflammatory signaling, endoplasmic reticulum stress, and epithelial responses may influence disease-associated changes in the prostate.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="research-card">
              <div class="icon">03</div>
              <h3>Fibrosis & Tissue Remodeling</h3>
              <p>We study stromal remodeling, collagen deposition, and epithelial-stromal communication to understand how tissue architecture changes during BPH.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

